item.title: Introduce Yourself
item.description: Photo by Faris Mohammed on Unsplash Growing up I read a lot of my dad’s books, especially those on Astronomy. I was in love with NASA, spacecrafts, star trek…all that good stuff. It was my dream to go to space someday and piss on the moon or something. Unknown photo credit via Gizmodo Ah! the good ol’ days. We had this desktop computer my dad bought and this piece of machinery was awesome to look at.
